title: 12/09/21 DPS Best Of

description:
On Today's Dan Patrick Show, DP talks to friend of the show Ross Tucker who will be on the radio call of Army/Navy this weekend. He explains why everyone should attend the game at least once in their life. And Warriors play-by play announcer calls to discuss Steph Curry's mission to break the all-time 3-point record.
